        To: Paul Burkey
      From: Andrew "Mushroom" Kellett
    
û
      Text: Well Paul, I hope you like this issue, as it has taken me a
            while to complete. I have reviewed some of your latest games
            in the REVIEWS section, so that may generate a bit more income
            for you to spend on Newcy Browns !!
    
            Thanx also for the compaction routines. They have really
            helped me out this issue, as I have been able to squeeze a lot
            more pictures into the issue without having to worry too much
            about space available on the disk.
    
            Well, I best go now, as I have about 25 more articles to write
            before I get anywhere near completed. Hope to hear from you
            again soon !
    
    
    
    
