û
      Text: Well, here it is. I hope you find this new and much improved
            system a much better and easier to use than the previous
            issues. Since Carl's demise from the EA team, a lot more work
            and effort has been put into creating this, as I don't have to
            rely on anyone else to provide valuable source for within the
            magazine itself.
    
            The goods don't stop here! Next issue see's the introduction
            of yet an even better text reader, which will allow text and
            images to be on-screen together, making articles much more
            interactive to read. I have not had enough time to develop the
            system fully for inclusion in this issue.
    
            Remember that EA is your disk magazine, full of the things
            which you would like to see in an AMOS magazine such as this.
            Please keep sending in your articles and suggestions, so we
            can keep improving the whole magazine. Please take the time to
